        "reaction_type_english": "Syngas to hydrocarbons reaction",
        "description": "在单一反应器中，使用CZA（甲醇合成催化剂）、A（甲醇脱水催化剂）和Cu/BEA（烃合成催化剂）组成的堆叠床催化剂体系，将合成气（H₂:CO = 2:1）在220°C、750 kPa条件下直接转化为C₄⁺烃类产物。考察了不同催化剂质量配比（3+1|1, 3+1|2, 3+1|3）对CO转化率、C₄⁺烃类产率和选择性的影响。",
        "text_snippet": "Systematic increases in the Cu/BEA catalyst mass, with constant CZA+A mass and constant total bed volume (by changing the mass of SiC diluent), provided a series of CZA+A|Cu/BEA compositions with mass ratios of 3+1|1, 3+1|2, and 3+1|3. Each composition was tested at the same reaction conditions from Section 3.2 (Table 2 and Figure 4).",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
    ]
